header.name: Sanctum of the Shadow Lady
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: Long after the Shadow Lady's defeat the sanctum remained uninhabited. Lately a band of hobgoblins rediscovered it. The sanctum of the Shadow Lady is a place of growth of a rare specie of blooms.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A rear entrance into the sanctum. A large stone double door with three keyholes to the east.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A basket with a leather armor.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: A key tucked under some debris.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A dying dwarf, a key among his belongings.

game_elements.name: Item 5
game_elements.description: A cape of magic missile locked in a magical safe.

game_elements.name: Item 6
game_elements.description: A mysterious, singing shield in a battered chest.

game_elements.name: Item 7
game_elements.description: A mutilated body of a hobgoblin, a key nearby.
